Mapdeck and tidycensus example

Kyle Walker

4/1/2020

library(tidycensus)
library(mapdeck)
options(tigris_use_cache = TRUE)

pct_over_65 <- get_acs(
  geography = "tract",
  variables = "DP05_0024P",
  state = "AZ",
  county = "Maricopa",
  geometry = TRUE
)

mapdeck(pct_over_65, 
        token = Sys.getenv("MAPBOX_TOKEN"),
        style = mapdeck_style("dark")) %>%
  add_polygon(fill_colour = "estimate",
              tooltip = "estimate", 
              legend = TRUE,
              legend_options = list(
                title = "% over age 65"
              ))
